            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"Experiment2\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('Experiment2', '0%')\" src=\"images/Mapswire/mapswire-continent_as-plain-map-asia-robinson-267_geolocation.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figura 2</b>: Medidas do tamanho da Terra por Eratóstenes e Al-Biruni. © Mapswire (<htcite0>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "dd4f3c8a-6624-4df5-93ac-37e0a4be9fdc",
                     "text": "Mapswire",
                     "page": "",
